ENTRY            G0101   20251208   20260508   20260508       G059
SUBENT        G0101001   20251208   20260508   20260508       G059
BIB                 13         21
TITLE      Isomeric ratios in the 12MeV bremsstrahlung-induced
            photonuclear reactions of europium isotopes: A study
            based on experiments and TALYS 2.0 calculations
AUTHOR     (Bui Minh Hue, Tran Duc Thiep)
INSTITUTE  (3VN IPH)
REFERENCE  (J,NIM/B,570,165949,2026)
FACILITY   (MICRT,4ZZZDUB) Electron accelerator Microtron MT-25
            of the Flerov Laboratory of Nuclear Reaction, Joint
            Institute for Nuclear Research, Dubna, Russia.
INC-SOURCE (BRST) Electron beam on 3 mm thick tungsten
            target
SAMPLE      Eu2-O3 foil (purity: 99.9%, a circular disc with a
            diameter of 1.5 cm,mass: 0.1766 g)
METHOD     (ACTIV,GSPEC) Irradiated for 7 h, 15 uA
DETECTOR   (HPGE) coaxial p-type HPGe detector (Canberra) with
            a diameter of 60.5 mm and a length of 31 mm
ANALYSIS   The external efficiency calibration method.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) counting statistics, detector efficiencies,
            and the intensities of the gamma-rays of interest.
STATUS     (APRVD) Approved by Bui Minh Hue (2025-12-09)
HISTORY    (20251208C) L.T.Anh and N. Otsuka
ENDBIB              21
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           24
